data.description: Unique is a term often cliched to describe real estate, so I'll let you discover the epitome of the word at 302 South St. If you possess a passion for individuality and crave opportunities to let creative juices flow, you're sure to have ideas for how you'll make this feel like home. You will enjoy living across the Neuse River from downtown New Bern! Ask your agent for disclosures and a copy of the full home inspection that has already been performed. No permit located for ''lookout'' room-not counted as living area. Flood Zone AE (no flooding since owner purchased). Priced to convey as-is.
